import React from 'react'
import Container from '@mui/material/Container'
import TextField from '@mui/material/TextField'

const Createstudent = () => {
  return (
        <>
         <TextField sx={{mb:1,mt:1}}
           id="name"
           label="Enter Name of student"
           variant='outlined'
           color='primary'
         />
         <TextField sx={{mb:1,mt:1}}
         id="name"
         label="Enter phone no:"
         variant='outlined'
         color='primary'
       />
       <TextField sx={{mb:1,mt:1}}
       id="name"
       label="Rollno"
       variant='outlined'
       color='primary'
     />
     <TextField sx={{mb:1,mt:1}}
     id="name"
     label="branch"
     variant='outlined'
     color='primary'
   />
</>
       
  )
}

export default Createstudent
